        "checksum": "c20bcfa265d6b61200dc66f789c00227d5e7092eafb9b667ae0d2a30de46ca48_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg9c11k6OTt_text": "<strong>Dr. Amara Reveals How to Quickly Implement Manifestation in Your Life</strong>",
        "ggHboygj04d_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">The one missing element most men overlook, and how you can direct the current of success, abundance &amp; purpose starting today.</span></p>",
